  npcVisitFlavors:
  - turns the names of common plants into something older and heavier.
  - says nothing, but the silence feels deliberate and companionable.
  - makes an offering of some kind. You are not entirely sure what.
  npcExchangeFlavors:
  - presses a lump of beeswax into your hands. Useful for many things they won't
    name directly.
  - places an antler talisman carefully in your palm, without explanation or ceremony.
